[[Afaylu:Ayatul Kursi by AbdurRahman Al Sudais.wav|thumb|''Ayat Alkursi'' s yils n limam [[Ɛabdurrahman Al Sudays]].]]'''Ayat Alkursi''' (s [[Tutlayt Taɛrabt|taɛrabt]]: آية الكرسي, <small>Taɣarast n tiɣri<abbr>.</abbr></small> ''’āyat al-kursī''‎) tga laya tis-255 ḥ ssura nḥ [[Takṭṭumt n tfunast|tkṭṭumt n tfunast]] ḥ [[Lqʷran|Lqqʷran]] lli d isggiz rbbi f urqqas nns [[Muḥammad]] {{saw}} taẓallit n rbbi fllas diyiḍ n Lqadr ḥ wayyur n Rmaḍan, ilkm uṭṭun n tassurin nns 114. Tga laya y'ad yat ḥ layat lli llanin ḥ tassurin n udlis n rbbi. Laya y'ad ar tinni mas rbbi yan ayga d ur illi ma tt irwasn.<ref> [https://quran.com/2/255?translations=131 "Surat Al Baqara"] . ''quran.com''. Retrieved 16 October2020.</ref> Ilkm wuṭṭun n twaliwin nns 50 n tawalt, ḥ kull tawalt tlla gis Lbrkt , lliḥ tggiz laya y'ad rwln ibalisn ,yssnti umzwaru n tassurt s yism n rbbi «''بسم الله»'' ,d anggaru nns s ism nns «''العلي العظيم»''.<ref>Abdullah Yusuf Ali (1983) <small>[First published 1934]</small>. ''The Holy Qur'ān: Text, Translation and Commentary''. Brentwood, Maryland: Amana Corp. pp. 102–103.</ref>

Laya y'ad tga yat laya bahra istawhman dar [[Lislam|imuslmn]] d tugt nnsn ḥfḍnt s wul nnsn.<ref>Seyyed Hossein Nasr, ed. (2018). ''The Study Quran''. HarperCollins Publishers. p. 110.</ref>

